{"word":"Galilee","slug":"galilee","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Galilee</b> <a href=\"#/H1551\">H1551</a> <br/> 1. The northern district of Palestine<br/> - A city of refuge in<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=20&verse=7'>Jos 20:7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=21&verse=32'>Jos 21:32</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=6&verse=76'>1Ch 6:76</a> <br/> - Cities in, given to Hiram<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=9&verse=12'>1Ki 9:12</a> <br/> - Taken by king of Assyria<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=15&verse=29'>2Ki 15:29</a> <br/> - Prophecy concerning<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=9&verse=1'>Isa 9:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=4&verse=15'>Mat 4:15</a> <br/> - Called Galilee of the Nations<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=9&verse=1'>Isa 9:1</a> <br/> - Herod, tetrarch of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=6&verse=21'>Mar 6:21</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=3&verse=1'>Luk 3:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=23&verse=7'>Luk 23:7</a> <br/> - Jesus resides in<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=17&verse=22'>Mat 17:22</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=19&verse=1'>Mat 19:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=7&verse=1'>Joh 7:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=7&verse=9'>Joh 7:9</a> <br/> - Teaching and miracles of Jesus in<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=4&verse=23'>Mat 4:23</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=4&verse=25'>Mat 4:25</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=15&verse=31'>Mat 15:31</a>; <a href='https://www.