.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=13&verse=3'>Mat 13:3</a> <br/> - Miracles of Jesus on<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=8&verse=32'>Mat 8:32</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=14&verse=33'>Mat 14:33</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=17&verse=27'>Mat 17:27</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=4&verse=39'>Mar 4:39</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=5&verse=9'>Luk 5:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=8&verse=24'>Luk 8:24</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=21&verse=11'>Joh 21:11</a> "}]}